{"tid":262805,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"翻過幾次教會，發覺唔係好嘢。","createTime":"2017-05-29T13:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T06:32:32.000Z","uid":69599,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15702437bb5de79810679e6f98ea020a420c0909","tid":262805,"uid":69599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:29:50.000Z","msg":"小學跟過朋友翻過幾次，後來嫌太悶就冇再去。<br />\n人大咗諗住再去睇下會唔會有唔同感受啦，<br />\n加上自己嗰排個人太易怒希望個人可以慈悲為懷包容一啲自己好討厭既人。<br />\n之後就跟咗朋友翻，一開始嗰到既人對你好好，覺得佢地好善良，覺得係信仰既原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後尾去既次數多咗聽到好多令我好質疑既嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地好中意要貶低其他宗教<br />\n會話人地係邪教<br />\n拜祖先都唔得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n重點係有啲所謂既基督徒其實都係有偽善既一面<br />\n所以我寧願都係做翻自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65b6fee8fabd64000148ce703466bb274fa9cbd","tid":262805,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:31:22.000Z","msg":"信得耶蘇都係身有屎啦"},{"pid":"ee5c95e98624334dddd280a38857b0912852311a","tid":262805,"uid":69599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:45:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信得耶蘇都係身有屎啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87d5247f8be7e378fc42cda582ca3b95c7b91d5c","tid":262805,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:48:44.000Z","msg":"無啦啦正正常常邊個會諗起耶蘇<br />\n做得陰濕野多心虛先拜依樣拜果樣"},{"pid":"26db25620ac7df21d6ddb097b1b437a4fb678b7d","tid":262805,"uid":21633,